data.description: Reside on the Southside in the sought-after Parkhurst neighborhood, just a stones throw away from Lake Padden. The main level showcases a chef's kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, complemented by a breakfast nook and a formal dining room. The open floor plan seamlessly connects these areas, leading to the welcoming living room, featuring a charming fireplace. The primary bedroom, boasting a spacious ensuite, is conveniently located on the main level. The office/den provides versatile space for various purposes. Enjoy the mature landscaping and a private fenced backyard.
